spec_data.Name: mediawiki-HTTP302Found
spec_data.Description:
Pushes a HTTP code 302 (Found) to the browser when there is a redirect instead
of handling it internally. The end user will not notice any difference (other
than the address to the page having an ?rd=Redirecting_page bit at the end).
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 07:22:13 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Forces an external HTTP 302 redirect instead of internal redirects
